des:
Thamtu products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your robot.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your robot- just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your robot name products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Thamtu" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "Thamtu" app;
(3). You need to have some Thamtu devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Thamtu" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Thamtu Home" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Thamtu Home" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Thamtu Home", and you'll be navigated to "Thamtu Home" login page;
(9). Input your Thamtu account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the robot.”
“Alexa, turn off the robot.”
